## AI-PLC Pipeline

This project uses AI-PLC (AI Product Lifecycle) as the primary workflow system.

### Quick Reference

- Workflow: Collection → Inception → Construction → Operation
- Skills: `.claude/skills/ai-plc/01-collection/SKILL.md` ~ `04-operation/SKILL.md`
- Rules: `.claude/rules/ai-plc-system.md`, `ai-plc-session.md`, `ai-plc-adaptive.md`

### Working Directory

Create new work in `Flow/[current-month]/[current-date]/`.

### Key Files

- `AGENTS.md` — Agent operational rules
- `.claude/rules/` — Modular operational rules
- `.claude/skills/ai-plc/` — 4-stage pipeline skills
